commit message: Fixed crash where the player tried to resume after a phonecall
Replaced all UI's with Fresco. Picasso is still used as backend in some locations
Fixed the palette for the TopPlayer
Do not call isPlaying if the player is not initialized
Ensured we only work with valid URLs.  And if we don't we catch potential exceptions and report them
Prevent crash when ACRA is not initialized in a reciever
Ensured that the VendorMediaCast unregisters it's recievers when the application is destroyed
Ignore META-INF/NOTICE.txt from all dependencies when building
Ensured Volley is kept alive in order to refresh subscriptinos when they are added
Do not use recycled bitmaps for the notification
